        "subtopic": "Why we use root word",
        "content": "• Root words help us understand the meaning of complex words by breaking them down into their basic components.\n• They provide clues about the meaning of unfamiliar words, making it easier to decipher their definitions.\n• Understanding root words can enhance vocabulary and improve language skills."
