    "topic": "3. Root Word - Phobia",
    "subtopics": [
      {
        "subtopic": "Phobia → Fear, Dislike (डर, नापसंद)",
        "content": "• MEANING:- fear, dislike (Greek origin)\n• अर्थ:- डर, नापसंद (यूनानी)\n\n• EXAMPLES:-\n1. Demophobia = demo (people) + phobia (fear) → fear of people/crowd (भीड़ से डर)\n2. Zoophobia = zoo (animals) + phobia (fear) → fear of animals (जानवरों से डर)\n3. Theophobia = theo (God) + phobia (fear) → fear of God/religion (ईश्वर से डर)\n4. Pedophobia = pedo (child) + phobia (fear) → fear/dislike of children (बच्चों से डर)\n5. Gynophobia = gyno (woman) + phobia (fear) → fear/dislike of women (महिलाओं से डर)\n\n• NOTE:- 'Phobia' always indicates an intense fear or dislike of something."
