    "topic": "5. Root Word - Bio",
    "subtopics": [
      {
        "subtopic": "Bio → Life (जीवन)",
        "content": "• MEANING:- life (Greek origin)\n• अर्थ:- जीवन (यूनानी)\n\n• EXAMPLES:-\n1. Biology = bio (life) + logy (study) → study of life (जीव विज्ञान)\n2. Biography = bio (life) + graphy (writing) → life story (जीवनी)\n3. Biodegradable = bio (life) + degrade (break down) → can be broken by living organisms (जैविक रूप से नष्ट होने योग्य)\n4. Antibiotic = anti (against) + bio (life) → medicine against bacteria (प्रतिजैविक)\n5. Biometrics = bio (life) + metrics (measurement) → measurement of life features (जैविक माप)\n\n• NOTE:- 'Bio' root always relates to life or living organisms."
