    "topic": "6. Root Word - Chron",
    "subtopics": [
      {
        "subtopic": "Chron → Time (समय)",
        "content": "• MEANING:- time (Greek origin)\n• अर्थ:- समय (यूनानी)\n\n• EXAMPLES:-\n1. Chronology = chron (time) + logy (study) → study of events in order of time (कालक्रम)\n2. Synchronize = syn (together) + chron (time) → happening at same time (एक साथ होना)\n3. Chronic = chron (time) → lasting for a long time (दीर्घकालिक)\n4. Anachronism = ana (against) + chron (time) → something out of its time (कालभ्रम)\n5. Chronicle = chron (time) + icle (record) → historical account of events (इतिहास विवरण)\n\n• NOTE:- 'Chron' root words always relate to time."
